1
00:01:44,150 --> 00:01:45,330
How did she find you?

2
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:47,260
She went to our hospital

3
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:49,330
with two old ladies, saying they were her neighbors.

4
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:51,050
She said they run a hospital.

5
00:01:51,070 --> 00:01:52,330
They wanted to treat the rheumatologist.

6
00:01:52,590 --> 00:01:55,490
But when they got there, they realized it's a cosmetic surgery clinic.

7
00:01:55,510 --> 00:01:57,290
So why'd you bring her home?

8
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:01,540
Let me explain something.

9
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:04,930
How has your mom been feeling?

10
00:02:06,510 --> 00:02:07,490
Why do you ask that?

11
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:09,610
She can eat and drink.

12
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:12,060
She looks fine, but

13
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:14,260
I think

14
00:02:14,590 --> 00:02:15,980
there might be something off.

15
00:02:17,750 --> 00:02:19,540
Can't you tell she's faking it?

16
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,850
Jingwen, I know you don't have a good relationship with your mom,

17
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:23,540
but she's so old.

18
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:25,660
You haven't eaten yet, have you?

19
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:26,660
Let me cook for you.

20
00:02:31,590 --> 00:02:32,060
Zhou Kai,

21
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:33,610
come to this address and pick up your mom.

22
00:02:34,150 --> 00:02:34,820
No need.

23
00:02:35,190 --> 00:02:36,850
I'll drive myself.

24
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:43,450
When did you get married?

25
00:02:43,590 --> 00:02:45,410
Why didn't you tell me?

26
00:02:45,710 --> 00:02:47,100
Is this your husband?

27
00:02:47,470 --> 00:02:48,980
Look at me, I should've dressed well.

28
00:02:53,870 --> 00:02:54,500
This is

29
00:02:55,870 --> 00:02:56,940
a wedding gift.

30
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:59,260
Can you stop messing around?

31
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,690
When are you having a baby?

32
00:03:06,150 --> 00:03:06,890
I'll help you take care of it,

33
00:03:06,910 --> 00:03:07,820
I have experience.

34
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:08,660
Look, little baby.

35
00:03:08,910 --> 00:03:09,890
Baby...

36
00:03:09,910 --> 00:03:11,220
When are you having a baby?

37
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:11,850
I'll help take care of it.

38
00:03:11,870 --> 00:03:12,940
Have you said enough?

39
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:15,290
Did you ever take care of me when I was little?

40
00:03:15,750 --> 00:03:16,690
Now you want me

41
00:03:16,710 --> 00:03:18,010
to be the dutiful daughter?

42
00:03:18,030 --> 00:03:19,450
Let me tell you, that's never gonna happen.

43
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:20,450
You stay here.

44
00:03:20,470 --> 00:03:20,940
Have Zhou Kai come pick you up.

45
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:22,100
Alright, Jingwen.

46
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,610
Stop running around.

47
00:03:29,630 --> 00:03:31,130
I'm so busy, and I had to come to pick you up.

48
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:33,410
Hello, I'm Qin.

49
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:36,890
I'm Jingwen's friend.

50
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,890
Is it okay if I talk to you for a moment?

51
00:03:40,030 --> 00:03:40,570
Come.

52
00:03:45,590 --> 00:03:47,730
Doesn't Auntie mental state seem a bit off?

53
00:03:47,750 --> 00:03:48,980
Did you have her checked?

54
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,170
She's always like this.

55
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:52,890
From now on...

56
00:04:01,430 --> 00:04:02,010
Charge!

57
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:14,100
Why is it always me they call

58
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:15,130
when something happens at school?

59
00:04:15,150 --> 00:04:16,540
You're not her guardian, are you?

60
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:18,660
I can't go,

61
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,170
I have surgery this afternoon.

62
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:24,050
Can you figure something out?

63
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:29,610
Where's the chili oil?

64
00:04:31,830 --> 00:04:32,780
I'm so flustered.

65
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:36,050
As expected, it's mala tang.

66
00:04:36,070 --> 00:04:37,780
I could smell it all the way down the hall.

67
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,340
What?

68
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,700
You don't have surgery this afternoon?

69
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:41,540
Just one more left this afternoon.

70
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:42,610
Let me try it.

71
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:46,100
Dr. Qiao.

72
00:04:46,630 --> 00:04:47,930
Come on, if you're gonna eat, sit properly.

73
00:04:47,950 --> 00:04:49,580
Come, sit.

74
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:52,780
It's all yours.

75
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:53,370
So good.

76
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:56,410
Aren't you eating?

77
00:04:56,430 --> 00:04:57,020
I will.

78
00:04:58,390 --> 00:04:59,100
Not bad, huh?

79
00:05:00,630 --> 00:05:01,580
Can you do me a favor?

80
00:05:05,160 --> 00:05:06,410
Of course, it's totally worth it.

81
00:05:06,430 --> 00:05:07,220
Definitely worth it.

82
00:05:08,070 --> 00:05:08,780
Here's the thing.

83
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:09,540
My daughter

84
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:11,810
has this really important performance at school.

85
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:13,250
They're asking parents to attend.

86
00:05:13,270 --> 00:05:15,100
I've missed it a few times already.

87
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:16,660
I can't miss it this time.

88
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:18,850
But I've got a liposuction this afternoon.

89
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:19,980
It's a very small case.

90
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,730
Can you help me out?

91
00:05:22,480 --> 00:05:23,460
Please.

92
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,930
I've got a breast augmentation at 2 p.m. this afternoon.

93
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:29,170
Then schedule hers for 4 p.m.

94
00:05:29,630 --> 00:05:30,490
4 p.m. this afternoon.

95
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:32,980
Nice.

96
00:05:33,430 --> 00:05:34,370
This place is pretty good.

97
00:05:34,390 --> 00:05:35,900
Add some chili oil.

98
00:05:39,480 --> 00:05:40,170
It's broken.

99
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:41,780
What happened?

100
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,250
Hurry, get a new one.

101
00:05:45,270 --> 00:05:45,900
Okay.

102
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:47,780
Manman,

103
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,220
go notify Zhong Shunhua.

104
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:50,730
She's Dr. Meng's patient.

105
00:05:50,750 --> 00:05:52,610
Her surgery might be delayed by an hour.

106
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:53,460
Got it.

107
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,540
Half an hour should be fine.

108
00:05:54,950 --> 00:05:56,410
Isn't half an hour a bit tight?

109
00:05:56,430 --> 00:05:58,290
We'll just finish our surgery in half an hour here.

110
00:05:58,310 --> 00:06:00,020
Stop nagging, hurry up.

111
00:06:01,630 --> 00:06:03,610
Right, remember to give Zhong Shunhua some IV fluids.

112
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:04,660
Got it.

113
00:06:05,390 --> 00:06:06,100
Is that so?

114
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:07,460
Sorry about this.

115
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:08,250
Ms. Qiao's been

116
00:06:08,270 --> 00:06:09,660
working non-stop all day.

117
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:11,580
To keep your surgery on schedule,

118
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:13,020
she's had to give up her rest time.

119
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:15,020
So, we hope you understand.

120
00:06:15,870 --> 00:06:16,850
Yes, I understand.

121
00:06:17,070 --> 00:06:18,220
You haven't eaten yet, right?

122
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:19,980
Let me have the nurse give you some fluids.

123
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:20,460
Thanks.

124
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:20,900
It's okay, no worries.

125
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:21,810
You can rest now.

126
00:06:22,870 --> 00:06:23,610
Wait,

127
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:26,220
can you just listen to me first?

128
00:06:26,560 --> 00:06:28,050
Just give me a straight answer, Dad.

129
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:30,290
Are you coming to my wedding or not?

130
00:06:31,070 --> 00:06:32,410
My Mom's definitely coming.

131
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:34,610
She's never missed an important moment in my life.

132
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:36,540
Are you wondering if Ze will be there?

133
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:37,700
He'll be there.

134
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:39,930
Let me put it this way,

135
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:42,220
Mom and Ze are practically joined at the hip now.

136
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,140
If Mom's there,

137
00:06:43,160 --> 00:06:44,410
Ze will definitely be there too.

138
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:49,220
Alright.

139
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:50,340
Fine, do whatever you want.

140
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:51,490
Gotta go.

141
00:06:52,270 --> 00:06:53,050
Dad's coming to the wedding.

142
00:06:53,070 --> 00:06:54,220
And he's bringing Auntie Wang with him.

143
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,850
Seriously?

144
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,810
You could've just let him come alone.

145
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:01,410
Why did you have to ask him to bring her?

146
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,610
How long has it been since we got divorced?

147
00:07:05,000 --> 00:07:07,780
If the management from the mine see this,

148
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,250
it's gonna be so awkward.

149
00:07:09,390 --> 00:07:10,540
Well, you're bringing Ze.

150
00:07:10,560 --> 00:07:12,370
Why can't Dad bring Wang?

151
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:13,540
I'm bringing Ze...

152
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:15,580
Isn't that what you were thinking deep down?

153
00:07:16,070 --> 00:07:17,490
He got divorced and found someone younger,

154
00:07:17,510 --> 00:07:18,490
big deal.

155
00:07:18,750 --> 00:07:19,730
It's not like you can't do the same.

156
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:20,850
Besides,

157
00:07:21,270 --> 00:07:23,980
if it really came down to a face-off between them,

158
00:07:24,310 --> 00:07:26,100
I'd bet on Ze winning.

159
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:26,610
Really?

160
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:27,610
Of course.

161
00:07:27,630 --> 00:07:29,540
Let's not talk about how he treats you,

162
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:31,170
or whether he's capable or not.

163
00:07:31,750 --> 00:07:32,930
But just in terms of looks,

164
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:34,460
he's definitely decent.

165
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:35,980
If Dad's meeting him for the first time,

166
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,660
It's totally normal for him

167
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:38,930
to feel a little intimidated.

168
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,610
Stop talking nonsense.

169
00:07:41,630 --> 00:07:44,140
I didn't choose Ze for those reasons.

170
00:07:44,870 --> 00:07:47,850
He really cares about me.

171
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,290
Give him a call.

172
00:07:50,310 --> 00:07:51,290
Ask him where he is.

173
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:55,370
What's going on?

174
00:07:55,390 --> 00:07:57,050
His phone keeps losing signal.

175
00:08:05,390 --> 00:08:07,220
Where the heck did he go?

176
00:08:07,630 --> 00:08:08,250
Xue,

177
00:08:08,270 --> 00:08:09,290
get me some chocolate.

178
00:08:19,390 --> 00:08:19,980
Mr. Qin,

179
00:08:21,070 --> 00:08:23,140
the implant broke during surgery today.

180
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:25,490
Shouldn't we check this new batch of products?

181
00:08:27,160 --> 00:08:27,900
Ms. Qiao, here you go.

182
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:30,980
Alright.

183
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,130
Ms. Qiao, I ordered takeout.

184
00:08:33,150 --> 00:08:33,850
-Just have some. - I don't have time.

185
00:08:33,870 --> 00:08:34,530
You guys eat.

186
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:38,650
Ms. Qiao, the waist binder!

187
00:08:42,630 --> 00:08:43,250
Manman,

188
00:08:43,550 --> 00:08:44,370
Is implant rupture

189
00:08:44,390 --> 00:08:46,420
a common issue in our hospital?

190
00:08:46,870 --> 00:08:49,060
It happens in about one out of ten cases.

191
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:53,650
Seems like we recently changed suppliers.

192
00:09:04,390 --> 00:09:05,420
Stop with the nonsense.

193
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:06,340
Where are you?

194
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,700
Don't you know my mom had surgery today?

195
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:11,610
She kept asking about you before the anesthesia.

196
00:09:11,870 --> 00:09:13,340
We called you a hundred times, and you didn't pick up.

197
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:15,730
Hold on.

198
00:09:17,030 --> 00:09:18,530
Doctor, was my mom's surgery successful?

199
00:09:19,030 --> 00:09:19,700
You are...?

200
00:09:20,030 --> 00:09:21,100
I'm Zhong Shunhua's daughter.

201
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:22,580
Yes, everything went well.

202
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:23,980
A total of 2000 milliliters were removed.

203
00:09:24,510 --> 00:09:26,180
She needs to wear a compression garment for three months.

204
00:09:26,670 --> 00:09:28,060
She can take a shower two days after the stitches are removed.

205
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:29,850
Soreness and swelling are normal.

206
00:09:30,150 --> 00:09:31,250
Especially when she sleeps,

207
00:09:31,270 --> 00:09:32,460
just let her find a comfortable position.

208
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:33,850
- Okay. - She shouldn't stay in one posture for too long,

209
00:09:33,870 --> 00:09:34,850
Or she might develop bedsores.

210
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,300
Okay, thank you, doctor.

211
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:37,250
Oh, this...

212
00:09:37,390 --> 00:09:38,610
Sorry, I'll clean it up right away.

213
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,010
Hello?

214
00:09:40,630 --> 00:09:43,130
You still have the time for a road trip in the suburbs?

215
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,370
What's the point of coming now?

216
00:09:44,390 --> 00:09:45,980
The surgery's already over.

217
00:10:00,390 --> 00:10:01,130
Damn it.

218
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:33,940
Hello?

219
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:35,130
Is this Manman?

220
00:10:35,600 --> 00:10:36,890
Yes, Ms. Qiao.

221
00:10:36,910 --> 00:10:39,530
How is Zhong Shunhua in Bed 13 doing?

222
00:10:42,030 --> 00:10:43,370
I just checked on her five minutes ago.

223
00:10:43,390 --> 00:10:44,370
Everything is normal.

224
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:46,010
Alright.

225
00:10:46,030 --> 00:10:47,010
Good.

226
00:10:47,390 --> 00:10:48,610
Can I trouble you to check on her

227
00:10:48,630 --> 00:10:50,300
every two hours tonight?

228
00:10:50,510 --> 00:10:51,340
No problem.

229
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:54,610
Ms. Qiao, is there something you're worried about?

230
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:56,650
Nothing in particular.

231
00:10:57,270 --> 00:10:58,770
Just want to be cautious.

232
00:10:59,240 --> 00:10:59,940
Alright.

233
00:11:09,390 --> 00:11:10,180
Look at this picture.

234
00:11:10,630 --> 00:11:11,250
It looks good.

235
00:11:11,600 --> 00:11:12,940
No way, I look too fat in this one.

236
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:14,060
You look great.

237
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:16,300
My daughter is beautiful no matter what.

238
00:11:19,150 --> 00:11:19,730
Hairuo,

239
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,530
did Ze tell you

240
00:11:21,550 --> 00:11:23,060
he's not coming tonight?

241
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:25,820
He clearly promised

242
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:27,730
he'd be here for my surgery.

243
00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:29,130
He told me

244
00:11:29,360 --> 00:11:30,610
there was a landslide.

245
00:11:30,630 --> 00:11:31,940
The roads were blocked, and he couldn't get out.

246
00:11:32,270 --> 00:11:33,610
They just got cleared today.

247
00:11:33,750 --> 00:11:35,300
By the time he gets to the city, it'll be too late,

248
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:36,580
so he's not coming.

249
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:37,460
A landslide?

250
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:39,300
Not sure if that's true or not.

251
00:11:39,670 --> 00:11:41,250
Is he okay?

252
00:11:41,750 --> 00:11:43,100
He's totally fine, jumping around like nothing happened.

253
00:11:44,390 --> 00:11:44,980
Mom,

254
00:11:45,510 --> 00:11:46,730
I can't help but feel like

255
00:11:46,750 --> 00:11:48,610
he never really wanted to come see you.

256
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:49,730
Don't talk nonsense.

257
00:11:51,030 --> 00:11:51,980
The doctor said

258
00:11:52,630 --> 00:11:55,060
my surgery isn't a big deal.

259
00:11:55,750 --> 00:11:57,220
If he doesn't wanna come, then forget it.

260
00:11:57,720 --> 00:11:59,460
As long as he shows up on the wedding day, that's enough.

261
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:01,130
Then you tell him.

262
00:12:01,510 --> 00:12:02,820
I think he's up to something.

263
00:12:02,840 --> 00:12:03,770
Alright,

264
00:12:03,790 --> 00:12:04,610
enough.

265
00:12:05,320 --> 00:12:06,370
I know what I'm doing.

266
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:09,130
Are you hungry?

267
00:12:09,150 --> 00:12:10,370
You haven't eaten all day.

268
00:12:10,630 --> 00:12:11,580
Have some food, come on.

269
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:12,730
I don't have an appetite.

270
00:12:16,030 --> 00:12:16,700
What's wrong?

271
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:17,890
It hurts again.

272
00:12:18,630 --> 00:12:19,980
Should I call the nurse?

273
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:21,460
No need.

274
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:23,010
The doctor said

275
00:12:23,670 --> 00:12:25,130
this kind of pain is normal.

276
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:27,610
Don't bother them.

277
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:29,370
Still, why go through

278
00:12:29,390 --> 00:12:30,610
all this suffering?

279
00:12:31,270 --> 00:12:33,010
You're just worried that during the wedding,

280
00:12:33,030 --> 00:12:35,010
Dad and Wang might steal the spotlight, right?

281
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:37,300
You want to stand next to Ze,

282
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:39,340
so you look more compatible and younger.

283
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:40,980
Like me.

284
00:12:42,550 --> 00:12:43,300
Oh, you think

285
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:44,530
