307
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:46,490
What's wrong with my mom?

308
00:13:46,510 --> 00:13:47,530
It hurts! Be gentle!

309
00:13:47,840 --> 00:13:48,300
How about here?

310
00:13:48,320 --> 00:13:48,890
Hurts!

311
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:49,770
Mom!

312
00:13:49,790 --> 00:13:51,100
Understood, I'll take her to the ER immediately.

313
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:52,250
Pack up quickly, we're transferring her to another hospital.

314
00:13:52,270 --> 00:13:53,370
Why do we have to transfer?

315
00:13:53,390 --> 00:13:54,530
Our equipment isn't sufficient.

316
00:13:54,550 --> 00:13:55,700
We need to transfer her as soon as possible!

317
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:57,490
Hurry up! Come and help!

318
00:13:58,150 --> 00:13:58,700
Mom!

319
00:14:02,480 --> 00:14:03,100
How is she?

320
00:14:03,360 --> 00:14:04,130
Ms. Qiao,

321
00:14:04,150 --> 00:14:05,700
Zhong Shunhua has been transferred to Jingbei Hospital.

322
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:06,530
She's in emergency treatment now.

323
00:14:06,550 --> 00:14:07,730
I've been monitoring the situation.

324
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:09,850
Why was she sent to Jingbei?

325
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:11,490
Her condition is too critical.

326
00:14:11,510 --> 00:14:12,770
You should come over first, we'll explain more then.

327
00:14:13,320 --> 00:14:14,420
Alright, I'm on my way.

328
00:14:17,240 --> 00:14:17,850
Hello,

329
00:14:18,320 --> 00:14:19,700
