330
00:14:19,720 --> 00:14:20,770
Her name is Zhong Shunhua.

331
00:14:21,510 --> 00:14:22,490
Could you check for me?

332
00:14:22,510 --> 00:14:23,940
Are you her family member?

333
00:14:24,630 --> 00:14:25,980
No, I'm her doctor.

334
00:14:26,750 --> 00:14:27,770
You performed the liposuction?

335
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:28,770
Yes.

336
00:14:29,670 --> 00:14:31,490
She now has intestinal perforation.

337
00:14:32,030 --> 00:14:33,250
Contact a larger hospital immediately.

338
00:14:33,270 --> 00:14:34,220
We're running low on blood.

339
00:14:34,240 --> 00:14:36,250
If this continues, she won't make it.

340
00:14:36,390 --> 00:14:36,890
Ms. Qiao,

341
00:14:36,910 --> 00:14:37,770
how did this happen?

342
00:14:38,150 --> 00:14:38,820
Hold on.

343
00:14:41,030 --> 00:14:41,850
This is Qiao Yang.

344
00:14:41,870 --> 00:14:43,100
