345
00:14:44,510 --> 00:14:45,610
I'll have Third Hospital set up a fast-track admission.

346
00:14:45,630 --> 00:14:46,650
Coordinate with them right away.

347
00:14:46,670 --> 00:14:47,340
Got it.

348
00:14:48,390 --> 00:14:48,980
Huang,

349
00:14:49,000 --> 00:14:49,770
I have a patient here

350
00:14:49,790 --> 00:14:50,700
