371
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:06,580
Mom...

372
00:16:17,480 --> 00:16:18,770
The surgical procedure was fine.

373
00:16:18,790 --> 00:16:20,100
A total of 2000ml was removed.

374
00:16:20,120 --> 00:16:21,250
