I just found out too.

380
00:16:35,480 --> 00:16:36,820
Does she have any chronic illnesses?

381
00:16:36,840 --> 00:16:37,300
Yes.

382
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:38,220
She has hypertension.

383
00:16:38,240 --> 00:16:39,770
She's been taking Shihuida regularly.

384
00:16:41,440 --> 00:16:43,100
