385
00:16:43,120 --> 00:16:44,530
Check if it's an intestinal perforation.

386
00:16:45,510 --> 00:16:47,010
Got it, thanks, Huang.

387
00:16:48,030 --> 00:16:48,980
Come on.

388
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:49,850
Almost there!

389
00:16:49,870 --> 00:16:51,010
Get the backboard ready.

390
00:16:51,030 --> 00:16:51,850
Backboard!

391
00:16:51,870 --> 00:16:53,060
Turn her over!

392
00:16:53,600 --> 00:16:54,370
- No! - Turn her over!

393
00:16:54,390 --> 00:16:55,340
Why are you yelling?

394
00:16:56,270 --> 00:16:57,180
Come on, turn her over.

395
00:16:59,080 --> 00:16:59,610
Mom!

396
00:17:00,320 --> 00:17:00,650
It hurts...

397
00:17:00,670 --> 00:17:01,250
Hang in there, dear.

398
00:17:01,270 --> 00:17:01,890
Just hold on a little longer, okay?

399
00:17:01,910 --> 00:17:03,060
Stay strong, Mom!

400
00:17:03,080 --> 00:17:03,530
Hang in there.

401
00:17:03,550 --> 00:17:04,810
I've got you, love.

402
00:17:04,830 --> 00:17:05,290
Hold her steady.

403
00:17:05,310 --> 00:17:06,730
Just a little longer.

404
00:17:07,030 --> 00:17:08,330
Huang, hurry up!

405
00:17:08,350 --> 00:17:09,570
Hang in there.

406
00:17:12,680 --> 00:17:13,620
Hold on, Mom!

407
00:17:13,640 --> 00:17:14,180
Come.

408
00:17:18,270 --> 00:17:18,810
Hello?

409
00:17:19,000 --> 00:17:19,570
Hello?

410
00:17:20,030 --> 00:17:21,980
Hairuo, what do you want this late?

411
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:23,050
There was a complication during my mom's surgery!

412
00:17:23,070 --> 00:17:23,980
Come here now!

413
00:17:24,680 --> 00:17:25,620
Is it serious?

414
00:17:25,640 --> 00:17:27,090
Yes, very serious!

415
00:17:27,110 --> 00:17:27,940
She's about to go into surgery!

416
00:17:27,960 --> 00:17:29,380
Come to Third Hospital now!

417
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:30,810
That's so far...

418
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:33,900
Even if I come now, I'd just be waiting around.

419
00:17:34,030 --> 00:17:34,730
Far?

420
00:17:34,750 --> 00:17:35,810
She's your wife!

421
00:17:35,830 --> 00:17:36,660
My mom's life is on the line,

422
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:37,730
and you're complaining about distance?

423
00:17:37,750 --> 00:17:39,330
Do you not care whether she lives or dies?

424
00:17:40,030 --> 00:17:40,700
Hairuo,

425
00:17:40,880 --> 00:17:42,250
can you calm down?

426
00:17:42,270 --> 00:17:43,330
Calm down?

427
00:17:43,510 --> 00:17:44,660
I'm asking you, are you coming or not?

428
00:17:44,680 --> 00:17:45,660
Can you come?

429
00:17:46,030 --> 00:17:46,770
I'll talk to him.

430
00:17:46,790 --> 00:17:47,770
None of your business.

431
00:17:48,000 --> 00:17:49,180
It's about your mother.

432
00:17:55,240 --> 00:17:55,940
Hello?

433
00:17:56,270 --> 00:17:57,700
This is Zhong Shunhua's doctor.

434
00:17:57,830 --> 00:17:59,010
She's in critical condition.

435
00:17:59,030 --> 00:18:00,220
We urgently need the spouse's signature.

436
00:18:00,550 --> 00:18:01,730
If you don't come, I'll call the police.

437
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:12,620
Ms. Qiao.

438
00:18:14,270 --> 00:18:14,860
Thank you.

439
00:18:14,880 --> 00:18:15,900
I'm sorry.

440
00:18:15,920 --> 00:18:17,460
It's my fault. I didn't ask enough questions

441
00:18:17,480 --> 00:18:18,860
before transferring her to Jingbei.

442
00:18:19,110 --> 00:18:20,380
I've caused you trouble.

443
00:18:20,550 --> 00:18:22,010
It's okay. You're new.

444
00:18:22,030 --> 00:18:23,250
Everyone makes mistakes.

445
00:18:23,270 --> 00:18:24,180
You can go home.

446
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:32,900
Are you afraid she'll hit me?

447
00:18:33,510 --> 00:18:34,380
I can take a beating.

448
00:18:35,880 --> 00:18:36,810
Go on, go home.

449
00:18:36,830 --> 00:18:37,570
Get some rest.

450
00:18:37,590 --> 00:18:38,220
Go.

451
00:18:38,510 --> 00:18:39,570
Go ahead.

452
00:18:57,350 --> 00:18:58,010
Hairuo!

453
00:18:58,240 --> 00:18:59,180
What's going on?

454
00:18:59,680 --> 00:19:00,660
Wasn't it far?

455
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:02,570
You got here in less than twenty minutes.

456
00:19:02,750 --> 00:19:04,380
I rushed like crazy!

457
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:06,220
Ran through red lights all the way here.

458
00:19:07,160 --> 00:19:08,570
Isn't this all for your mom?

459
00:19:08,960 --> 00:19:09,810
How is she now?

460
00:19:10,160 --> 00:19:11,380
She should be fine, right?

461
00:19:11,400 --> 00:19:12,770
How would I know?

462
00:19:12,790 --> 00:19:14,730
Wasn't this supposed to be a routine surgery?

463
00:19:14,880 --> 00:19:16,460
And with such a renowned doctor, too.

464
00:19:16,640 --> 00:19:17,620
How did it turn out like this?

465
00:19:21,790 --> 00:19:22,460
Who's that?

466
00:19:23,550 --> 00:19:24,620
The one who just mentioned calling the police?

467
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:27,220
Is Zhong Shunhua's family here?

468
00:19:27,240 --> 00:19:27,770
Yes.

469
00:19:29,480 --> 00:19:30,940
The X-ray results are out.

470
00:19:31,110 --> 00:19:32,380
It's not a bowel perforation from liposuction.

471
00:19:32,750 --> 00:19:33,530
A gastric hemorrhage?

472
00:19:34,750 --> 00:19:35,860
She needs immediate surgery.

473
00:19:36,030 --> 00:19:37,730
But the patient's condition is critical.

474
00:19:37,920 --> 00:19:39,330
We'll do everything we can to save her.

475
00:19:39,920 --> 00:19:41,380
But you should also be prepared for the worst.

476
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:41,980
Doctor,

477
00:19:42,070 --> 00:19:43,380
money doesn't matter.

478
00:19:43,480 --> 00:19:44,290
Her life is the most important thing.

479
00:19:44,550 --> 00:19:45,700
Huang, please help.

480
00:19:45,830 --> 00:19:46,460
I'll do my best.

481
00:19:46,830 --> 00:19:48,460
Doctor, please, save my mom!

482
00:19:48,590 --> 00:19:49,380
She hasn't even seen me get married yet!

483
00:19:49,400 --> 00:19:50,220
We'll do our best.

484
00:19:50,240 --> 00:19:51,140
Calm down.

485
00:19:51,160 --> 00:19:52,050
We'll do our best.

486
00:19:52,070 --> 00:19:52,980
Calm down.

487
00:19:53,070 --> 00:19:53,980
Pease.

488
00:19:54,000 --> 00:19:55,010
Don't touch me!

489
00:19:55,310 --> 00:19:56,530
Stop pretending to be the good guy.

490
00:19:57,000 --> 00:19:58,090
This isn't over!

491
00:19:58,550 --> 00:19:59,620
- Doctor, please! - Okay.

492
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:00,620
Just come with me and sign the form.

493
00:20:00,790 --> 00:20:01,330
Alright.

494
00:20:02,310 --> 00:20:02,900
Just you wait.

495
00:20:27,960 --> 00:20:28,530
Qiao Yang,

496
00:20:30,070 --> 00:20:31,090
still trying on wedding dresses?

497
00:20:31,640 --> 00:20:32,620
Come to the hospital now.

498
00:20:43,750 --> 00:20:44,460
Where's my mom?

499
00:20:46,590 --> 00:20:47,090
Mom!

500
00:20:50,270 --> 00:20:50,570
Mom!

501
00:20:50,590 --> 00:20:51,290
She needs immediate surgery.

502
00:20:51,310 --> 00:20:52,620
Please step aside.

503
00:20:53,200 --> 00:20:53,700
Don't worry.

504
00:20:54,200 --> 00:20:54,660
She'll be fine.

505
00:20:54,680 --> 00:20:55,620
Please move aside, thank you.

506
00:20:55,640 --> 00:20:56,380
Mom, it's okay.

507
00:20:56,790 --> 00:20:58,010
Mom.

508
00:20:58,750 --> 00:20:59,660
Mom.

509
00:20:59,680 --> 00:21:00,570
We need to begin surgery.

510
00:21:00,590 --> 00:21:01,940
Please move aside!

511
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:07,090
Family members, please wait outside.

512
00:21:07,110 --> 00:21:08,050
It's okay.

513
00:21:08,310 --> 00:21:09,330
- Mom. - It's okay.

514
00:21:11,510 --> 00:21:13,330
- Mom. - It's okay.

515
00:21:13,350 --> 00:21:14,140
It's okay.

516
00:21:14,640 --> 00:21:15,220
It's gonna be okay.

517
00:23:28,070 --> 00:23:28,860
Fancy some tofu pudding?

518
00:23:31,750 --> 00:23:32,700
What are you doing here?

519
00:23:33,310 --> 00:23:34,220
Came to check on you.

520
00:23:36,680 --> 00:23:37,730
Not eating? No appetite?

521
00:23:38,400 --> 00:23:39,220
Look over there.

522
00:23:43,070 --> 00:23:44,530
Wait, isn't it usually the longer your surgeries last,

523
00:23:44,550 --> 00:23:45,660
the hungrier you get?

524
00:23:46,790 --> 00:23:48,220
Remember back when we had that back-to-back shift

525
00:23:48,240 --> 00:23:48,980
with Qi Dacheng?

526
00:23:49,000 --> 00:23:51,090
We worked nonstop and then had a late-night barbecue.

527
00:23:51,510 --> 00:23:52,810
What, are you fasting today?

528
00:23:54,830 --> 00:23:55,490
What?

529
00:23:57,440 --> 00:23:58,490
What's wrong?

530
00:24:04,590 --> 00:24:05,730
Brought you some daily essentials.

531
00:24:06,750 --> 00:24:07,700
Figured you might need them.

532
00:24:08,640 --> 00:24:10,530
I reviewed your upcoming surgery plans.

533
00:24:10,790 --> 00:24:12,380
If there's anything you need to hand over, just tell me.

534
00:24:12,400 --> 00:24:13,380
I'll help coordinate things.

535
00:24:31,000 --> 00:24:33,530
Operating Room 1: Surgery for Zhong Shunhua is complete.

536
00:24:41,110 --> 00:24:42,420
Doctor! How's my mom?

537
00:24:44,440 --> 00:24:46,700
The gastric bleeding was caused by a stress ulcer.

538
00:24:46,720 --> 00:24:47,730
Her condition has stabilized.

539
00:24:47,750 --> 00:24:49,050
Can I see her?

540
00:24:49,070 --> 00:24:50,180
She's still unconscious.

541
00:24:50,750 --> 00:24:52,090
After surgery, she'll be transferred to the ICU

542
00:24:52,110 --> 00:24:53,050
for monitoring.

543
00:24:53,720 --> 00:24:55,250
Whether she wakes up or not

544
00:24:55,270 --> 00:24:56,860
depends on her recovery.

545
00:24:58,000 --> 00:24:59,770
How did she suddenly have gastric bleeding?

546
00:25:00,790 --> 00:25:01,620
It's all her fault!

547
00:25:01,750 --> 00:25:02,460
She wouldn't let my mom eat!

548
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:03,010
Calm down!

549
00:25:03,030 --> 00:25:04,460
The surgery was delayed by thirty minutes.

550
00:25:05,110 --> 00:25:06,810
The surgery was delayed?

551
00:25:07,200 --> 00:25:08,180
Was she given IV fluids in the meantime?

552
00:25:09,270 --> 00:25:09,860
Yes.

553
00:25:10,680 --> 00:25:11,980
Then it shouldn't have had much impact.

554
00:25:12,070 --> 00:25:13,980
Stress ulcers can have multiple triggers.

555
00:25:14,440 --> 00:25:16,140
Given your mom's condition,

556
00:25:16,160 --> 00:25:17,460
the primary factors would likely be

557
00:25:17,480 --> 00:25:19,700
anesthesia stress, surgical stress,

558
00:25:19,720 --> 00:25:21,010
severe emotional strain,

559
00:25:21,310 --> 00:25:21,940
or depression.

560
00:25:21,960 --> 00:25:23,420
All of these are possibilities.

561
00:25:24,200 --> 00:25:25,250
Think of it

562
00:25:25,270 --> 00:25:27,250
as the body's natural physiological response

563
00:25:27,270 --> 00:25:28,810
to external stimuli.

564
00:25:29,640 --> 00:25:30,810
It's just that this time,

565
00:25:31,200 --> 00:25:33,050
your mom's reaction was too severe.

566
00:25:34,550 --> 00:25:36,420
So basically, you're saying she was just unlucky?

567
00:26:11,160 --> 00:26:11,860
Dr. Zhou,

568
00:26:12,160 --> 00:26:13,660
does everything have to be removed?

569
00:26:14,030 --> 00:26:15,730
The area on my forehead, after removal, it's sunken in.

570
00:26:15,750 --> 00:26:16,860
It looks terrible.

571
00:26:17,720 --> 00:26:19,620
I told you during the consultation.

