00:42:14,190 --> 00:42:15,900
has been there watching over things for three days straight.

854
00:42:16,230 --> 00:42:17,420
She stayed with the resuscitation team,

855
00:42:17,800 --> 00:42:20,380
brought in the best gastroenterologists in the country,

856
00:42:20,400 --> 00:42:21,530
they've all seen what she's done.

857
00:42:22,070 --> 00:42:24,170
And her mother is still in critical condition.

858
00:42:24,590 --> 00:42:26,130
She doesn't have the time or energy to settle scores with her.

859
00:42:27,590 --> 00:42:28,490
So now,

860
00:42:29,150 --> 00:42:30,740
you're finally going back to Gemu, right?

861
00:42:31,630 --> 00:42:32,820
Gemu needs you.

862
00:42:33,880 --> 00:42:35,820
I feel like I need to split myself in half.

863
00:42:36,320 --> 00:42:38,530
The Starlight Project has just started,

864
00:42:38,920 --> 00:42:40,010
I can't just leave it behind.

865
00:42:42,030 --> 00:42:44,210
I thought I was getting a long vacation.

866
00:42:44,920 --> 00:42:46,820
Turns out it was just a short break.

867
00:42:50,320 --> 00:42:51,050
Back to the hospital?

868
00:42:53,150 --> 00:42:53,740
Yeah.

869
00:42:54,150 --> 00:42:55,820
New doctors have joined recently.

870
00:42:56,440 --> 00:42:57,570
I have to go check on them.
